<p:sld xmlns:a="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships" xmlns:p="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/presentationml/2006/main"><p:cSld><p:spTree><p:nvGrpSpPr><p:cNvPr id="1" name=""/><p:cNvGrpSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvGrpSpPr><p:grpSpPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="0" y="0"/><a:ext cx="0" cy="0"/><a:chOff x="0" y="0"/><a:chExt cx="0" cy="0"/></a:xfrm></p:grpSpPr><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="214" name="PlaceHolder 1"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="title"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="335880" y="352800"/><a:ext cx="11519640" cy="719640"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom><a:noFill/><a:ln w="0"><a:noFill/></a:ln></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr lIns="91440" tIns="45720" rIns="91440" bIns="45720" anchor="ctr"><a:noAutofit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr indent="0" algn="l" defTabSz="914400"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="90000"/></a:lnSpc><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2930" b="0" u="none" strike="noStrike" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="0099CC"/></a:solidFill><a:effectLst/><a:uFillTx/><a:latin typeface="Arial"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック Medium"/></a:rPr><a:t>Conclusion</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="2930" b="0" u="none" strike="noStrike" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="0099CC"/></a:solidFill><a:effectLst/><a:uFillTx/><a:latin typeface="Arial"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="216" name="TextBox 3"/><p:cNvSpPr txBox="1"/><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="731520" y="1400760"/><a:ext cx="10728720" cy="4600000"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom><a:noFill/><a:ln w="0"><a:noFill/></a:ln></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr lIns="90000" tIns="45000" rIns="90000" bIns="45000" anchor="t" wrap="square"><a:normAutofit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0" defTabSz="457200"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="104000"/></a:lnSpc><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="1100"/></a:spcAft></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1500" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="3A3838"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>Feasibility. </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1500" b="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="3A3838"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>A custom Griffin precompile makes PLUM verification run on a personal device where it otherwise does not finish. Without it the verification exhausts memory after 7.08 billion guest cycles; with it the verification proves on SP1 at 125.5 million cycles, a 56-fold cycle reduction, in roughly 15 to 30 minutes at 18.67 GB on a 24 GB laptop.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0" defTabSz="457200"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="104000"/></a:lnSpc><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="1100"/></a:spcAft></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1500" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="3A3838"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>The precompile paradox. </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1500" b="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="3A3838"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>Even with the bespoke chip in place, the algebraic hash is slower than a standard one. The Griffin precompile runs at 1.13 times the cycles of a software SHA-3 control at matched security, and the trace-area cost model accounts for the sign. Arithmetising a 199-bit-field algebraic hash through a custom chip costs more than a hash the substrate already supports.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="0" indent="0" defTabSz="457200"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="104000"/></a:lnSpc><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="1100"/></a:spcAft></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1500" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="3A3838"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>The evaluation finding. </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1500" b="0" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="3A3838"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>In our evaluations, neither general-purpose zkVM we tested produced a complete post-quantum zero-knowledge proof of PLUM verification. SP1 completes the proof, but the receipt it produces is not zero-knowledge, and the wraps that add zero-knowledge are pairing-based and so not post-quantum. RISC Zero is post-quantum and its whitepaper describes zero-knowledge by design, yet our prove run did not complete, it ended in a segment-verifier rejection at around 4.7 billion execute cycles, and RISC Zero disclaims a formal zero-knowledge guarantee for its deployed receipts.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="2" name="PlaceHolder 2"/><p:cNvSpPr txBox="1"><a:spLocks/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="8217720" y="6356520"/><a:ext cx="2588400" cy="364680"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom><a:noFill/><a:ln w="0"><a:noFill/></a:ln></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr lIns="91440" tIns="45720" rIns="91440" bIns="45720" anchor="ctr"><a:noAutofit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr algn="r"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" b="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>Waseda University Sako Laboratory</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="3" name="PlaceHolder 3"/><p:cNvSpPr txBox="1"><a:spLocks/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="10988640" y="6356520"/><a:ext cx="822960" cy="364680"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom><a:noFill/><a:ln w="0"><a:noFill/></a:ln></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr lIns="91440" tIns="45720" rIns="91440" bIns="45720" anchor="ctr"><a:noAutofit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr algn="r"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" b="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>Page </a:t></a:r><a:fld id="{A54637BD-B8CF-4D3B-B42A-BD4EF6700298}" type="slidenum"><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" smtClean="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Arial Nova"/><a:ea typeface="游ゴシック"/></a:rPr><a:t>19</a:t></a:fld></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:sld>
